<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><meta charset="utf-8">{{> base-styles}}</head>
<body>
  <div class="sheet">
    {{> letterhead}}

    <div class="doc-head">
      <div class="doc-eyebrow">To Whomsoever It May Concern</div>
      <h1 class="doc-title">Internship Certificate</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="meta-row">
      <div>
        <span class="meta-k">Reference No.</span>
        <span class="meta-v">{{refNo}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="right">
        <span class="meta-k">Date of Issue</span>
        <span class="meta-v">{{generatedDate}}</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>
        This is to certify that <strong>{{fullName}}</strong> successfully completed an
        internship with <strong>{{companyName}}</strong> as an
        <strong>{{jobTitle}}</strong> in the <strong>{{department}}</strong> department
        from <strong>{{joinDate}}</strong>{{#if lastWorkingDay}} to <strong>{{lastWorkingDay}}</strong>{{/if}}.
      </p>
      <p>
        During the internship, {{firstName}} was actively involved in real-world projects
        and demonstrated a keen willingness to learn, strong analytical ability, and a
        professional attitude. {{firstName}} was a sincere and enthusiastic intern who
        contributed positively to the team.
      </p>
      <p>
        We appreciate {{firstName}}'s efforts and wish {{firstName}} the very best for
        future academic and professional endeavours.
      </p>

      <div class="sign">
        <p style="margin:0 0 6px; font-size:10px; color:var(--muted);">For {{companyName}},</p>
        <div class="sign__space"></div>
        <div class="sign__rule"></div>
        <div class="sign__name">{{signatoryName}}</div>
        <div class="sign__title">{{signatoryTitle}}</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {{> footer}}
  </div>
</body>
</html>
